    "body": "@nicolasnoble Using prefix variable doesnot create so's linking properly.\r\nExample: \r\n`make install`\r\nOutput: `ldd libgrpc++_reflection.so.1.12.1`\r\n`\tlinux-vdso.so.1 =>  (0x00007fff289cd000)\r\n\t\r\n        libpthread.so.0 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libpthread.so.0 (0x00007f688f357000)\r\n\t\r\n        libgrpc++.so.1 => /usr/local/lib/libgrpc++.so.1 (0x00007f688f0fe000)\r\n\t\r\n        libstdc++.so.6 => /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libstdc++.so.6 (0x00007f688ed7c000)\r\n\t\r\n        libgcc_s.so.1 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libgcc_s.so.1 (0x00007f688eb66000)\r\n\r\n\tlibc.so.6 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libc.so.6 (0x00007f688e79c000)\r\n\r\n\t/lib64/ld-linux-x86-64.so.2 (0x00007f688f937000)\r\n\r\n\tlibgrpc.so.6 => /usr/local/lib/libgrpc.so.6 (0x00007f688e2ff000)\r\n\r\n\tlibm.so.6 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libm.so.6 (0x00007f688dff6000)\r\n\r\n\tlibrt.so.1 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/librt.so.1 (0x00007f688ddee000)\r\n`\r\nExample with prefix variable:\r\n`make install prefix=/foo/bar`\r\nOutput: `ldd libgrpc++_reflection.so.1.12.1`\r\n`\t\r\n        linux-vdso.so.1 =>  (0x00007ffd27ff5000)\r\n\r\n\tlibpthread.so.0 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libpthread.so.0 (0x00007fce60130000)\r\n\r\n\tlibgrpc++.so.1 => not found\r\n\r\n\tlibstdc++.so.6 => /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libstdc++.so.6 (0x00007fce5fdae000)\r\n\r\n\tlibgcc_s.so.1 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libgcc_s.so.1 (0x00007fce5fb98000)\r\n\r\n\tlibc.so.6 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libc.so.6 (0x00007fce5f7ce000)\r\n\r\n\t/lib64/ld-linux-x86-64.so.2 (0x00007fce60710000)\r\n\r\n\tlibm.so.6 => /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libm.so.6 (0x00007fce5f4c5000)\r\n`"
