    "body": "As I said, when you do `make install` on the system in the normal location, your system's `ldconfig` tool will find the libraries and link them appropriately. You simply need to learn and use this tool accordingly with your environment.\r\n\r\nPlease read the following documentation to learn about how this works:\r\nhttp://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man8/ldconfig.8.html\r\n"
